N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.4 - Quality

State Regulations

The product for sale under a trademark label must be in
conformity with applicable trademark grade standards adopted in accordance with
the provisions of article 12-A of the Agriculture and Markets Law. Such
standards shall be available for public insepction at the principal office of
the department. Notes
